                            <comment id="17199798" author="jark" created="Tue, 22 Sep 2020 04:37:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for reporting this &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=xiaozilong&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;xiaozilong&quot;&gt;xiaozilong&lt;/a&gt;. This is a bug in &lt;tt&gt;AvroSchemaConverter.convertToSchema&lt;/tt&gt;, the &lt;tt&gt;rowTypeCounter&lt;/tt&gt; is still possible to be duplicate which causes this problem. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
